name: Silverpop Link Clean Up
notes: There are several emails in Silverpop that contain "&email=%%EMAIL%%" in the URL. This part of the URL needs to be removed as it's pulling email address into the URL query string, which is considered PII (personally identifiable information). I've attached an excel file that contains a list of known email names in Silverpop (column C) and the links in question.
